The code snippet does not include checks to validate the length of incoming packets before processing them. It focuses on route validation but does not perform any checks to ensure that the packet structures being accessed are of sufficient length. Therefore, it does not contain similar solution behaviors as those mentioned in the vulnerability knowledge for CVE-2016-6162.

